        "body": "# Implement Automated Testing for Installation Scripts #4\r\n\r\n## 🎯 What This PR Does\r\n\r\nThis PR implements a complete automated testing framework for PrismOS installation scripts, addressing issue #4.\r\n\r\n## ✅ Features Implemented\r\n\r\n### 1. Testing Framework\r\n- **pytest** testing framework configured\r\n- **7 automated tests** covering critical functionality\r\n- **Test directory structure** with unit and integration tests\r\n\r\n### 2. Test Coverage\r\n- **File existence checks** - Verify installation scripts exist\r\n- **File permission validation** - Ensure scripts are executable\r\n- **Script syntax validation** - Check bash script syntax\r\n- **Safe installation simulation** - Dry-run integration tests\r\n\r\n### 3. CI/CD Pipeline\r\n- **GitHub Actions workflow** for automated testing\r\n- **Runs on every push and pull request**\r\n- **Ubuntu Linux test environment**\r\n\r\n### 4. Documentation\r\n- **TESTING.md** - Comprehensive testing guide\r\n- **Test runner script** - Simplified test execution\r\n- **Implementation summary** - Detailed overview of changes\r\n\r\n## 🧪 Test Results\r\nAll 7 tests are passing:\r\n- 3 basic file checks\r\n- 2 script syntax validations  \r\n- 2 integration tests\r\n\r\n## 🚀 How to Use\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# Run all tests\r\npython3 -m pytest tests/ -v\r\n\r\n# Run with test runner\r\npython3 run_tests.py\r\n\r\n# View CI results in GitHub Actions\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Continuous integration pipeline added to automatically run tests on code changes\n  * Added comprehensive unit tests validating script syntax, permissions, and presence\n  * Added integration tests for install script verification and behavior\n\n* **Documentation**\n  * Testing documentation guide added\n\n* **Chores**\n  * Project configuration files added\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
